  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Engineering Technician (Penjuru)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Ensure all internal calibrated equipments are calibrated on time.</p></li><li><p>Ensure all external calibrated equipments are arranged and calibration coordinated without delay.</p></li><li><p>Ensure all calibration work instructions are aligned with standard industry calibration method.</p></li><li><p>To manage the calibration system efficiently. Such as updating of calibration masterlist, calibration reports availability and accountability of the calibration equipments.</p></li><li><p>In charge of document control function.</p></li><li><p>Ensure all documents related to QMS systems are controlled, updated and published.</p></li><li><p>Monitor on the plant's clean room condition to ensure the particle count of clean rooms are performed as per schedule or ad hoc basis.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum Diploma or Higher NITEC in Engineering</p></li><li><p>Minimum 2 years calibration of testing equipment experience</p></li><li><p>Certificate in Statistical Process Control, MSA</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office, Google Drive</p></li></ul>",
